DataTypes.name: ADAS
DataTypes.description: Antilock Braking System signals.

DataTypes.name: Acceleration
DataTypes.description: Spatial acceleration.

DataTypes.name: Angular Velocity
DataTypes.description: Spatial rotation.

DataTypes.name: Average Speed
DataTypes.description: Average speed for the current trip.

DataTypes.name: Body
DataTypes.description: All body components of a vehicle

DataTypes.name: Cabin
DataTypes.description: All in-cabin components, including doors of a vehicle

DataTypes.name: Cargo Volume
DataTypes.description: The available volume for cargo or luggage. For automobiles, this is usually the trunk volume.

DataTypes.name: Chassis
DataTypes.description: All data concerning steering, suspension, wheels, and brakes.

DataTypes.name: Connectivity
DataTypes.description: Connectivity data

DataTypes.name: Curb Weight
DataTypes.description: Vehicle curb weight, including all liquids and full tank of fuel, but no cargo or passengers.

DataTypes.name: CurrentLocation
DataTypes.description: The current latitude and longitude of the vehicle.

DataTypes.name: Current Overall Weight
DataTypes.description: Current overall Vehicle weight. Including passengers, cargo and other load inside the car.

DataTypes.name: Driver data
DataTypes.description: Driver monitoring data when driving the vehilce

DataTypes.name: Emissions CO2
DataTypes.description: The CO2 emissions

DataTypes.name: Exterior
DataTypes.description: Information about exterior measured by vehicle.

DataTypes.name: GrossWeight
DataTypes.description: Curb weight of vehicle, including all liquids and full tank of fuel and full load of cargo and passengers.

DataTypes.name: Height
DataTypes.description: Overall vehicle height.

DataTypes.name: IsAutoPowerOptimize
DataTypes.description: Auto Power Optimization Flag When set to 'true', the system enables automatic power optimization, dynamically adjusting the power optimization level based on runtime conditions or features managed by the OEM. When set to 'false', manual control of the power optimization level is allowed.

DataTypes.name: IsBrokenDown
DataTypes.description: Vehicle breakdown or any similar event causing vehicle to stop on the road, that might pose a risk to other road users. True = Vehicle broken down on the road, due to e.g. engine problems, flat tire, out of gas, brake problems. False = Vehicle not broken down.

DataTypes.name: IsMoving
DataTypes.description: Indicates whether the vehicle is stationary or moving.

DataTypes.name: Length
DataTypes.description: Overall vehicle length.

DataTypes.name: LowVoltageBattery
DataTypes.description: Signals related to low voltage battery.

DataTypes.name: LowVoltageSystemState
DataTypes.description: State of the supply voltage of the control units (usually 12V).

DataTypes.name: MaxTowBallWeight
DataTypes.description: Maximum vertical weight on the tow ball of a trailer.

DataTypes.name: MaxTowWeight
DataTypes.description: Maximum weight of trailer.

DataTypes.name: OBD
DataTypes.description: OBD data

DataTypes.name: PowerOptimizeLevel
DataTypes.description: Power optimization level for this branch/subsystem. A higher number indicates more aggressive power optimization. Level 0 indicates that all functionality is enabled, no power optimization enabled. Level 10 indicates most aggressive power optimization mode, only essential functionality enabled.

DataTypes.name: Powertrain
DataTypes.description: Powertrain data for battery management, etc.

DataTypes.name: RoofLoad
DataTypes.description: The permitted total weight of cargo and installations (e.g. a roof rack) on top of the vehicle.

DataTypes.name: Service
DataTypes.description: Service data.

DataTypes.name: Speed
DataTypes.description: Vehicle speed.

DataTypes.name: StartTime
DataTypes.description: Start time of current or latest trip, formatted according to ISO 8601 with UTC time zone.

DataTypes.name: Trailer
DataTypes.description: Trailer signals.

DataTypes.name: TraveledDistance
DataTypes.description: Odometer reading, total distance traveled during the lifetime of the vehicle.

DataTypes.name: TraveledDistanceSinceStart
DataTypes.description: Distance traveled since start of current trip.

DataTypes.name: TripDuration
DataTypes.description: Duration of latest trip.

DataTypes.name: TripMeterReading
DataTypes.description: Trip meter reading.

DataTypes.name: TurningDiameter
DataTypes.description: Minimum turning diameter, Wall-to-Wall, as defined by SAE J1100-2009 D102.

DataTypes.name: VehicleIdentification
DataTypes.description: Attributes that identify a vehicle.

DataTypes.name: Width
DataTypes.description: Overall vehicle width.

DataTypes.name: WidthExcludingMirrors
DataTypes.description: Overall vehicle width excluding mirrors, as defined by SAE J1100-2009 W103.

DataTypes.name: WidthFoldedMirrors
DataTypes.description: Overall vehicle width with mirrors folded, as defined by SAE J1100-2009 W145.

DataTypes.name: WidthIncludingMirrors
DataTypes.description: Overall vehicle width including mirrors, as defined by SAE J1100-2009 W144.
